===References===
*[[Strong's concordance]] number:  [http://www.biblestudytools.net/Lexicons/Greek/grk.cgi?number=1839&version=kjv G1839] 

===Pronunciation===
*ἐξίστημι / existēmi / ex-is'-tay-mee
=== Etymology ===

*From [[ἐκ]] {{GG|1537}} and [[ἵστημι]] {{GG|2476}}; 
=== Verb ===
to put (stand) out of wits, that is, [[astound]], or (reflexively) become astounded, insane: - [[amaze]], be (make) astonished, be beside self (selves), [[bewitch]], [[wonder]].